TITLE: Node.js Server for Handling File Uploads from Expo FileSystem
DESCRIPTION: This Node.js server example demonstrates how to handle both binary and multipart file uploads from Expo applications. It uses Express and multer to process and save uploaded files to the server's filesystem.
