TITLE: Configuring ReactNativeTracing to Fix Development Server Issues
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript code to prevent Sentry from creating spans for log requests to the development server, which can cause transactions to never finish when using expo-dev-client.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bluesky-social/expo/blob/main/docs/pages/guides/using-sentry.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import * as Sentry from 'sentry-expo';
import Constants from 'expo-constants';

Sentry.init({
  tracesSampleRate: 1.0,
  integrations: [
    new Sentry.Native.ReactNativeTracing({
      shouldCreateSpanForRequest: url => {
        return !__DEV__ || !url.startsWith(`http://${Constants.expoConfig.hostUri}/logs`);
      },
    }),
  ],
});
```

