TITLE: Expanded iOS Build and Test Workflow
DESCRIPTION: Detailed YAML configuration for building and testing an iOS app, expanding the 'eas/maestro_test' function into individual steps. It includes installing Maestro, starting an iOS simulator, installing the app, running tests, and uploading artifacts.
