TITLE: Importing Tailwind CSS in Expo Entry Point - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Ensures CSS generated by Tailwind is dynamically loaded in the main entrypoint of the Expo/React Native web application, supporting hot module reloads. Uses Node.js 'require.context' to import CSS from the Tailwind cache directory. Dependency: correct path resolution, hot module replacement enabled. Input is runtime JS, output is globally available CSS classes.
