TITLE: Performing Schema-only Validation with Schemer
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how to validate data against a schema without additional asset validation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/bluesky-social/expo/blob/main/packages/@expo/schemer/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const validator = new Schemer(require('schema.json'));
try {
  await validator.validateSchemaAsync(require('data.json'));
} catch (e) {
  console.error(e);
}
